<P>
Photo, Spray from a broken water pipe arches onto the San Diego Freeway and 
across the southbound lanes in Huntington Beach, slowing traffic to a crawl. 
DAVID MURONAKA / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Alden Dias, water district employee, 
twists valve to shut off flow of water. 
</P>
